      <h2 style="color: #064e3b; font-size: 2.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 800;">Tree Authority in {cityData.City}</h2>
      <div style="background: white; border-radius: 24px; padding: 3rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; line-height: 1.9; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); position: relative;">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: -15px; left: 30px; background: #ea580c; color: white; padding: 5px 20px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.8rem;">LOCAL SPECIALIST: {focusService.toUpperCase()}</div>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #1b4332; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">{cityData.Description}</p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4b5563;">
            In <strong>{cityData.City}</strong>, specialized knowledge of <strong>{treeType}</strong> is essential. Whether you are near <strong>{landmark}</strong> or in the surrounding area, our network ensures every project is completed with local expertise and strict adherence to Florida's safety standards.
        </p>
